Positive Effects of Social Media on Humans:

Improved communication and connectivity
Increased access to information and news
Facilitated social and political movements
Platform for creative expression and networking opportunities

Negative Effects of Social Media on Humans:

Cyberbullying and harassment
Spread of misinformation and fake news
Addiction and time distraction
Impact on mental health and well-being

Ways to Improve Social Media:

Enhanced content moderation to combat harmful behavior
Transparent algorithms to provide clarity on content curation
User empowerment through customizable filters and preferences
Strengthened privacy measures and data protection
Promoting digital well-being with usage management features
Encouraging authenticity and discouraging fake accounts
Promoting digital literacy and critical thinking skills
Collaborating with experts and communities for user well-being
